      "raw_text": "Governor Hay has sent letters to\nthe boards of county commissioners\nin eastern Washington. calling at\ntention to the importance of the\nfifth sessions of the Dry Farming\ncongress at Spokane, October to 6.\nand urging them to give it every\nsupport. Governor Hay is a mem\nDer of the Washington board of CON\ntroll, which has charge of the ar\nrangements for the convention and\nthe international exposition of dry\nfarmed products in connection. Oc-\ntober 3 TO S. He is keenly inter\nested in the dry farming movement,\nbelieving that every community will\nbe benefited by the practice of mod\nern methods of cultivation."
    }
